Fish Tales Market & Eatery is the oldest Fish Market and Restaurant in Marathon. Located in the "Heart of the Florida Keys", Fish Tales is not only a full service fish house, offering fresh fish, shrimp, stone crab, lobster and other local seafood, but hand cut aged choice and prime steaks as well. Homemade Bratwurst and Italian Sausage, cheeses, salsa and spreads are also available. Having a special get together? We can make up a party platter, or offer recipe ideas.
​
Fish Tales serves up seafood "fresh from our market to your table", as well as burgers, steaks and homemade daily specials using only the freshest ingredients.
/$
About Us
$
$
AMAZING SANDWICHES
/$
$
We pride ourselves in providing the best seafood products from the Florida Keys. Stop by and try some of our Award Winning Conch Salad, Fritters and Chowder, Lobster Bisque, George’s smoked fish spread, whole fresh key lime pie or Chef Johnny’s Rambler Sandwich, which was voted best fish sandwich in Marathon.
/$

FRESH SEAFOOD
/$
$
This family-owned and operated landmark is the real deal.  Serving up the freshest, tastiest fish sandwiches around with a unique menu of Florida-inspired plates, original signature dishes and lots of daily specials.
​
Great German & Craft beers on tap, along with a terrific retail market featuring fresh seafood, meats & Certified Hand-Cut Angus Beed.
​
Keep this one in your back pocket!
​
-Travelhost // Florida Keys & Key West
